lead_paragraph: Arsenal kept up their bid for a hat-trick of FA Cup trophies, marching into the quarter-finals as Olivier Giroud and Theo Walcott netted twice in a 4-0 replay win at second-tier Hull City on Tuesday.

headline.main: Doubles for Giroud, Walcott as Arsenal Reach Last Eight
headline.print_headline: Doubles for Giroud, Walcott as Arsenal Reach Last Eight
